00:39:42,680 --> 00:39:43,400
Fine.

851
00:39:44,630 --> 00:39:45,510
Mother.

852
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:47,660
Yes.

853
00:39:48,510 --> 00:39:49,110
When a woman

854
00:39:49,110 --> 00:39:50,590
becomes a mother,

855
00:39:51,920 --> 00:39:53,030
she radiates

856
00:39:53,030 --> 00:39:54,470
a kind of great power.

857
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:56,060
Look at you.

858
00:39:56,510 --> 00:39:58,240
The way you're looking at me now

859
00:39:58,430 --> 00:39:58,920
has become like

860
00:39:58,920 --> 00:40:00,200
that of a lioness.

861
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:07,320
Liang Xiang,

862
00:40:08,150 --> 00:40:10,360
don't think that because
you hold a high position,

863
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:10,680
you can

864
00:40:10,680 --> 00:40:12,340
speak in such a flippant tone.

865
00:40:13,470 --> 00:40:14,400
To be honest,

866
00:40:15,200 --> 00:40:16,110
in my eyes,

867
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:17,550
you're not much better

868
00:40:17,550 --> 00:40:19,080
than that military student

869
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:20,590
on the ship.

870
00:40:21,500 --> 00:40:22,500
People like you

871
00:40:22,820 --> 00:40:24,420
are a dime a dozen in history.

872
00:40:25,590 --> 00:40:27,510
With power and interests in hand,

873
00:40:28,490 --> 00:40:30,750
you're still no different from the rest.

874
00:40:31,110 --> 00:40:31,590
You're still

875
00:40:31,590 --> 00:40:33,590
making the same historical mistakes.

876
00:40:33,590 --> 00:40:35,240
Apart from showing off

877
00:40:35,320 --> 00:40:36,120
in front of me,

878
00:40:36,240 --> 00:40:36,880
I don't see

879
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:38,680
any other progress you've made.

880
00:40:39,110 --> 00:40:40,150
Don't take your power and interests

881
00:40:40,150 --> 00:40:41,010
too seriously.

882
00:40:41,470 --> 00:40:42,150
You should feel guilty

883
00:40:42,150 --> 00:40:43,680
that the country has become

884
00:40:43,930 --> 00:40:45,530
like this  because of you all.

885
00:40:47,470 --> 00:40:49,070
Look at your flowery outfit.

886
00:40:49,430 --> 00:40:50,690
What does it amount to?

887
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,210
It'll all be nothing in the end.

888
00:40:56,270 --> 00:40:57,790
What do you mean, Shuhong?

889
00:40:58,400 --> 00:40:59,070
Your reckless words

890
00:40:59,070 --> 00:40:59,800
will affect

891
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:01,400
your beloved's reputation.

892
00:41:02,590 --> 00:41:03,470
You are now the wife of

893
00:41:03,470 --> 00:41:05,030
the Sixth Division's commander.

894
00:41:05,030 --> 00:41:06,030
Every word you say

895
00:41:06,110 --> 00:41:06,840
represents

896
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:08,570
his attitude and his position.

897
00:41:09,430 --> 00:41:10,400
I am myself,

898
00:41:10,720 --> 00:41:12,350
and my husband is my husband.

899
00:41:13,220 --> 00:41:14,620
It's just a bit of advice.

900
00:41:15,360 --> 00:41:16,760
Why use it to threaten me?

901
00:41:23,630 --> 00:41:24,630
Tufang's here?

902
00:41:25,110 --> 00:41:26,310
Why don't you come in?

903
00:41:28,110 --> 00:41:29,880
I don't think that's necessary.

904
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:30,810
Commander Yang,

905
00:41:32,030 --> 00:41:33,030
at three o'clock this afternoon,

906
00:41:33,030 --> 00:41:36,030
the entire division will load up
and head to Yongping.

907
00:41:36,470 --> 00:41:37,370
Don't be late.

908
00:41:48,820 --> 00:41:50,080
What did you say to him?

909
00:41:50,590 --> 00:41:51,990
Why does he seem so angry?

910
00:41:54,340 --> 00:41:54,970
Nothing.

911
00:41:55,420 --> 00:41:57,020
I just asked him about my son.

912
00:42:14,800 --> 00:42:16,550
Kaizhi, you really are something.

913
00:42:16,550 --> 00:42:18,880
We're having the autumn military drill
and Fenglan is here too.

914
00:42:18,880 --> 00:42:19,400
Why don't you let Shuhong

915
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:20,730
stay for a few more days?

916
00:42:21,680 --> 00:42:22,770
She's seen what she needed to see,

917
00:42:22,770 --> 00:42:24,430
and we've had our affectionate moments.

918
00:42:24,430 --> 00:42:26,960
She has matters to attend to
back in Shanghai.

919
00:42:28,070 --> 00:42:29,600
What time is the next train?

920
00:42:29,920 --> 00:42:30,920
5:11.

921
00:42:33,200 --> 00:42:34,920
You must accompany her
and see her onto the train.

922
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:36,580
You don't need to tell me that.

923
00:42:37,590 --> 00:42:38,740
Attention!
